OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCITV 1 playout fault disrupts
OL,4,Cregional and national news
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn some parts of the country, the early
OL,7,Fevening regional and national news
OL,8,Fprogrammes on ITV 1 were disrupted by a
OL,9,Fswitching issue at the channel playout
OL,10,Ffacility operated by Red Bee.
OL,12,FViewers of ITV 1 in Yorkshire, West
OL,13,FEngland, South England, London, North
OL,14,FWest England, North East England,
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, Wales and the Channel
OL,16,FIslands saw only a portion of their
OL,17,Frespective regional news programmes.
OL,23,EPub: 06-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14202
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCITV 1 playout fault disrupts
OL,4,Cregional and national news
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe national ITV News programme that
OL,7,Ffollowed was also disrupted in most of
OL,8,Fthe affected regions ` London being the
OL,9,Fmain exception, where the national
OL,10,Fprogramme was broadcast in its
OL,11,Fentirety.
OL,13,FBut the national news programme failed
OL,14,Fto appear at all in many of the
OL,15,Fregions.
OL,17,FReports online suggest the issue was
OL,18,Fcaused by a switching failure at the
OL,19,FITV playout centre operated by Red Bee.
OL,23,EPub: 06-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14203
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCITV 1 playout fault disrupts
OL,4,Cregional and national news
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe problems started when many regions
OL,7,Ffailed to switch to their regional news
OL,8,Fprogrammes. An ITV 1 breakfiller loop
OL,9,Fappeared instead.
OL,11,FMany of the affected regions crashed
OL,12,Finto their regional programme, minutes
OL,13,Flate, when the weather forecast was in
OL,14,Fprogress.
OL,16,FA second switching failure meant many
OL,17,Fregions were unable to switch away from
OL,18,Ftheir regional studio back to the
OL,19,Fnational schedule.
OL,23,EPub: 06-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14204
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCITV 1 playout fault disrupts
OL,4,Cregional and national news
OL,5,
OL,6,FConsequently, output from the regional
OL,7,Fstudios remained on air for quite some
OL,8,Ftime beyond the regional news slot.
OL,10,FMost of the affected regions quickly
OL,11,Fput up an animated version of their
OL,12,Frespective ITV regional logos; some
OL,13,Fremained on their programme endboards.
OL,15,FOne-by-one, the affected regions began
OL,16,Fto switch back to the national
OL,17,Fschedule, with the final region
OL,18,Frestored to normal shortly after 7pm,
OL,19,Fminutes into an edition of The Chase.
OL,23,EPub: 06-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14205
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCITV 1 playout fault disrupts
OL,4,Cregional and national news
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe handful of ITV 1 regions that were
OL,7,Flargely unaffected by the problems will
OL,8,Fhave heard an apology at 6.40pm and 7pm
OL,9,Fby the live network ITV 1 announcer.
OL,11,FSTV (in Scotland) ` which has its own
OL,12,Fplayout operation and is run
OL,13,Findependently of ITV plc (which runs
OL,14,Fthe ITV franchises in England, Wales
OL,15,Fand Northern Ireland) ` is believed to
OL,16,Fhave been unaffected by the playout
OL,17,Ffault at Red Bee.
OL,23,EPub: 06-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
